::Divebomb::

Divebomb snipes off three missiles with his particle rifle, and he 
taps the last missile on the side, with , deflecting it. "Ha, stupid 
Gestalt," The missile circles, and nails him in the back, knocking 
him out of the sky. He struggles to recover, and does so, swooping 
close to the ground, and away from Element(G).
